  <source>Acucela Inc.</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the safety and efficacy of 2% rebamipide compared to
      placebo in clearing of fluorescein staining of the central cornea in subjects with dry eye
      disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
